text: Vengadathanpatti (Tamil:வெங்கடதாம்பட்டி is a village located in the Krishnagiri district of Tamil Nadu, India. It is located from the head postal office in Uthangarai.Vengathanpatti also called as Vengadathampatti. == See also == *Category:Villages in Krishnagiri district *வேங்கடதம்பட்டி ஊராட்சி == References == Category:Villages in Krishnagiri district
title: Vengadathanpatti
